This repository contains demonstrative materials for the Digital Product Passport
(DPP) for textile products under EU regulation ESPR (UE) 2024/1781.

The data shown in the demos is fictional and generated for illustrative purposes.
It does not represent the operational reality of any brand, supplier or
certification body cited (in particular, "Confecciones Atlantico S.A." and other
suppliers are fictional). The simulated GTINs (e.g. 8412345678035) are not
registered with AECOC.

Public web data extracted from ternua.com is used under fair use for technical
demonstration of how a real product can be mapped into a DPP structure. Ternua
Group S.L. is the rightful owner of the underlying product information.

Code, JSON-LD schemas and HTML templates produced by Code Contract S.L. are
released under the following terms:

- Reuse for non-commercial educational, research and regulatory-preparation
